menu "SVC-100 Control"

config SVC_USE_LOGIC_ENGINE
    bool "Use the IF/FOR/THEN logic engine for relay control (review-gated)"
    default n
    help
        When enabled, control.c drives relays via the components/logic engine
        (presence/digital-input conditions with FOR dwell, OFF-delay linger, and
        OFF interlocks) and applies the SVC-012 dry-contact presence fallback.

        DEFAULT OFF. The legacy per-rule evaluator remains the production path
        until this integration is signed off on the bench. Do NOT enable for a
        production build without Codex review and bench validation.

endmenu
